### Pokemon Attachments Router API
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001/api/v0
@workflowId = pokemon

# -----
# Image Execution
# -----

### Execute with image (uses URL or local file via ref)
# @name executeImage
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/{{workflowId}}/executions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "input": {
    "kind": "image",
    "ref": "media/pikachu.png"
  }
}

### Get image execution by ID
@imageExecId = {{executeImage.response.body.data.exec_id}}
GET {{baseUrl}}/executions/workflows/{{imageExecId}}
Accept: application/json

